265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasserman explained that they originally planned to have a stuntman do most of the sequence in a balaclava, but the actor wanted to do it himself.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.999597940192419, \"rank\": 0.0003990964416970377, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"About five minutes into the presentation [Tom Cruise] goes, 'I am in.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am only doing it if I get to do everything,'\\\" Wasserman said.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.999597940192419, \"rank\": 0.0003990964416970377, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise has famously done all of his own stunts in recent years, including the exhilarating mountain jump in 2023's \\\"Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One,\\\" so it's unsurprising that he wanted to do the sequence.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the LA28 chief said he did the whole thing for free, according toThe Hollywood Reporter.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1386, \"end\": 1395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999996878159, \"rank\": 3.0943871303989336e-10, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is a little surprising given the logistics of filming the separate jumps in Paris and Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1488, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999472493, \"rank\": 5.267179919524818e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999994029839817, \"rank\": 5.969907117946594e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasserman explained that the star was filming thenext \\\"Mission: Impossible\\\" movieat the time, but managed to squeeze in the Olympics jump.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.999597940192419, \"rank\": 0.0003990964416970377, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He finished filming Mission: Impossible at 6 p.m. in London, got right on a plane.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 173